    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes the OSPFv3 graceful restart.  The OSPFv3 graceful restart is identical to that of OSPFv2 except for the differences described in this document.  These differences include the format of the grace Link State Advertisements (LSAs) and other considerations. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
